    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208570/extras/6c3dd2ba249f91c08dc99b6d44998a02.avif?t=1745510243\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208570/extras_big/6c3dd2ba249f91c08dc99b6d44998a02.avif?t=1745510243 width=800 height=151 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Geyserlands </i>is a deck-building game of modern otherworldly mystery. You are a detective just assigned to a national park nobody knows exists.  Gain new cards and upgrade your deck as you explore the mystery of <i>Geyserlands</i>. Unlock secret powers and gain special advantages.  But delve too deep and <i>Geyserlands</i> will consume you.  How will your story end in <i>Geyserlands</i>?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208570/extras/e5ebe321dee58ee14b74c47529a27305.avif?t=1745510243\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3208570/extras_big/e5ebe321dee58ee14b74c47529a27305.avif?t=1745510243 width=800 height=151 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build a deck from hundreds of cards that tell the story of your character's history, abilities, insights and connections.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the cards you draw each turn to solve some of <i>Geyserlands</i>' hundreds of mysteries.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve mysteries to earn new and better cards and remove weaker cards from your deck.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Escape despair and death with a variety of upgradable healing cards that prevent <i>Geyserlands</i> from consuming you.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn strange powers and supernatural edges that allow you to push your luck and accomplish the impossible.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unravel the secrets of <i>Geyserlands</i>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However your story ends, you will gain new cards for your next journey.</p></li></ul>",
